metadata.name: Mighty Moles #1
metadata.description: The Mighty Moles are remarkable critters are known for their intelligence, craftiness, and unwavering work ethic. However, their journey hasn't been easy - they were once enslaved and confined in cramped, dark, and damp conditions while they tirelessly generated billions for CZ. Yet, these Mighty Moles have bravely escaped their past and are now in search of new Mine Bosses. With their sights set on a brighter future, these Mighty Moles are eagerly striving to mine heaps of Ethereum for their new owners.
